name: Head Soccer Pix
description:
Head soccer but pixel.

Player 1(Messi) controller:"W " for jump,"D" for right and "A" for left movemenet. Also "C" shoot up & "V" shoot down.

Player 2(Ronaldo) controller:"up arrow " for jump,"right arrow" for right and "left arrow" for left movemenet. Also "M" shoot up & "N" shoot down.

you can double jump for twice tick.

dont touch Quit button.
